<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOUR EARTHQUAKES RATTLE DEVASTATED IRANIAN TOWN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NICOSIA, Cyprus 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Iranian town of Roudbar, devastated by an earthquake on June 21, was shaken 
by four quakes overnight, the Official Islamic News Agency reported Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
It said there was no immediate report of casualties or damage. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
