ORANGE COUNTY -- ATHLETICS; HIGH SCHOOL ATHLETICS; FOOTBALL TEAMS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA090390-0098 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 271004 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 3, 1990, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
