IMMIGRATION; RELOCATION OF PEOPLE; CONCENTRATION CAMPS; CANADA -- IMMIGRATION; 
DEPORTATION; SCIENTISTS; INVESTIGATIONS; MORALITY; CONFLICT OF INTEREST; SPACE 
PROGRAMS -- UNITED STATES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
